<subSubSection pageId="6" pageNumber="186" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="6.[136,1452,767,974]" pageId="6" pageNumber="186">
<location LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:039287B9FFDFFFA2FF43FD06FB68FC3F:8EE46074FFDFFFA2FF43FD6EFF7FFCE8" box="[136,180,767,793]" country="Saint Helena, Ascension and Tristan da Cunha" county="We" municipality="April" name="The" pageId="6" pageNumber="186">The</location>
original specimen (
<emphasis box="[399,532,768,793]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="186">Martius s.n.</emphasis>
) was collected in 
<collectingMunicipality box="[729,791,767,793]" pageId="6" pageNumber="186">April</collectingMunicipality>
, in the state of Bahia. 
<bibRefCitation author="Cunha, M. C. S." box="[1032,1186,767,794]" pageId="6" pageNumber="186" pagination="5 - 41" refId="ref7419" refString="Cunha, M. C. S. (1985) Revisao das especies do genero Luehea Willd. (Tiliaceae), ocorrentes no estado do Rio de Janeiro. Sellowia, Anais Botanicos do Herbario Barbosa Rodrigues 37: 5 - 41." type="journal article" year="1985">
<collectingCountry box="[1032,1105,767,793]" name="Saint Helena, Ascension and Tristan da Cunha" pageId="6" pageNumber="186">Cunha</collectingCountry>
(1985)
</bibRefCitation>
indicated a specimen in M as the 
<typeStatus box="[234,335,803,829]" pageId="6" pageNumber="186">holotype</typeStatus>
, but it was neither seen nor specifically identified. 
<collectingCounty box="[890,927,804,830]" pageId="6" pageNumber="186">We</collectingCounty>
found only 
<specimenCount box="[1057,1209,803,830]" pageId="6" pageNumber="186" type="generic">one specimen</specimenCount>
of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Martius" authorityYear="1826" box="[1242,1345,803,829]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Malvaceae" genus="Luehea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malvales" pageId="6" pageNumber="186" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="villosa">
<emphasis box="[1242,1345,803,829]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="186">L. villosa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
collected by 
<collectorName box="[171,258,839,865]" pageId="6" pageNumber="186">Martius</collectorName>
(
<emphasis box="[275,314,840,865]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="186">s.n.</emphasis>
) and preserved in 
<collectorName box="[524,680,839,866]" pageId="6" pageNumber="186">Herbarium M</collectorName>
, where his collection is located (
<bibRefCitation author="Stafleu, F. A. &amp; Cowan, R. S." box="[1047,1310,839,866]" pageId="6" pageNumber="186" refId="ref8497" refString="Stafleu, F. A. &amp; Cowan, R. S. (1976 - 1988) Taxonomic Literature: A selective guide to botanical publications and collections with dates, commentaries and types, 2 nd ed., Smithsonian Libraries, last updated 28 Jun. 2012. https: // doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. title. 48631" type="book" year="1976">Stafleu &amp; Cowan 1976</bibRefCitation>
–1988: 325). 
<collectorName box="[136,173,876,902]" pageId="6" pageNumber="186">We</collectorName>
accept it as the 
<typeStatus box="[350,448,875,901]" pageId="6" pageNumber="186">holotype</typeStatus>
of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Martius" authorityYear="1826" box="[484,588,875,901]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Malvaceae" genus="Luehea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malvales" pageId="6" pageNumber="186" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="villosa">
<emphasis box="[484,588,875,901]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="186">L. villosa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, since it has the original data of the protologue and the identification with the handwriting of 
<collectorName box="[311,478,911,937]" pageId="6" pageNumber="186">Martius. There</collectorName>
are no duplicates in other herbaria. 
<collectorName box="[889,957,911,937]" pageId="6" pageNumber="186">Based</collectorName>
on our study of this collection, we confirm this name as a heterotypic synonym of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Martius" authorityYear="1826" box="[574,717,947,973]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Malvaceae" genus="Luehea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malvales" pageId="6" pageNumber="186" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="candicans">
<emphasis box="[574,717,947,973]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="186">L. candicans</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, as previously accepted by 
<bibRefCitation author="Burret, K. E. M." box="[1026,1183,947,974]" pageId="6" pageNumber="186" pagination="592 - 880" refId="ref7098" refString="Burret, K. E. M. (1926) Beitrage zur Kenntnis der Tiliaceen. Notizblatt des Botanischen Gartens und Museums zu Berlin-Dahlem 9 (88): 592 - 880. https: // doi. org / 10.2307 / 3994327" type="journal article" year="1926">Burret (1926)</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
